details.codeExample:
// React / Next.js
const crdtElement = client.getCrdtElement();
// Flush CRDT edit activities after 30 seconds of inactivity
crdtElement.setActivityDebounceTime(30000);

// Other Frameworks
const crdtElement = Velt.getCrdtElement();
crdtElement.setActivityDebounceTime(30000);

import { CrdtActivityActionTypes } from '@veltdev/react';

// Type-safe filtering of CRDT activities
const activities = activityElement.getAllActivities({
  actionTypes: [
    CrdtActivityActionTypes.EDIT,
  ],
});

deltas.releaseNoteText:
Exported constant objects (`CommentActivityActionTypes`, `RecorderActivityActionTypes`, `ReactionActivityActionTypes`, `CrdtActivityActionTypes`) and their union types provide type-safe action type values for use in [`ActivitySubscribeConfig`](/api-reference/sdk/models/data-models#activitysubscribeconfig) filters and custom activity creation. Use these instead of raw strings when filtering by `actionTypes`.

```ts
const activities = activityElement.getAllActivities({
  actionTypes: [
    CommentActivityActionTypes.ANNOTATION_ADD,
    CommentActivityActionTypes.STATUS_CHANGE,
  ],
});
```

